title: Medieval Dining Room Interior (Assets Pack/Modular): 122 Unique Meshes
description: An Aestethic Architectural setting set in Ancient Greece. Romantic and Comfy feel might suit parties, partners, and families.
longDescription:
MEDIEVAL DINING ROOM INTERIOR Remastered: Version 3.0.3


[Updates: 25th December 2023]

Project Now Supports Both Version: UE 4.27.2 and UE 5.1.1


Showcase: https://youtu.be/FlOXn3d91eE?si=zDNhVQvVaS16YM0T

Essential Features: https://youtu.be/rv1K2Q9EG_8?si=fsNg-CH5HwWEa2GC

Doc: https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1suX8uXGY9ky7iJnwgxbkGFZE3G8YUDSNTIF8tdJjSU4/edit?usp=sharing


What's New in Remastered 3.0.3 Updates?

+ Added 9 New Blueprints:

  • Individual Wooden Floor Variety Packs
  • Fireplace Tessellation
  • Pile of Gold Salute D'or
  • Ancient Greece Bean Porridge
  • Roasted Chicken
  • Roasted Corn
  • Cheese Breads
  • Ancient Knife
  • Hanging Medieval Water Gourd
  • Fruit Basket with Cloth
  • Hanged Giant Anchor
  • Hanged Rope Tied
  • Artificial Flower Vine
  • Curtain Cloth Simulation (Both UE4 & UE5 Support their own physics as well: NvCloth & Chaos)

+ Added 3 New Particle Systems:

  • Candle Fire Normal & Large
  • Medieval Realistic Bonfire Normal & Large
  • Medieval Realistic Dust

+ Mesh Refinement, UVs, & Textures:

  • Medieval Rocking Chair Model (More Accurate with Natural Humanoid Sat Posture)
  • Veggies Rack Textures
  • Fruit Basket Model
  • Fireplace Set (with Tessellation)

+ Added Skeletal Meshes & Physics:

  • Artificial Flower Vine
  • Hanged Giant Anchor
  • Medieval Rocking CHair
  • Single Curtain Cloth
